<pre>
{
  "extends": ["eslint:recommended", "plugin:prettier/recommended"],
  "env": { "node": true, "es2021": true },
  "parserOptions": { "ecmaVersion": "latest" }
}
</pre>
Que signifie l'extension <code>"plugin:prettier/recommended"</code> ?
